This paper is primarily focused on secure information flow analysis, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also introduces a novel type system for enforcing access control in Android applications, which falls under the category of programming languages (cs.PL) and software engineering (cs.SE). The paper presents a type inference algorithm, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and systems and control (cs.SY).
